item.title: MatSE Graduation Lunch
item.description: The Department of Materials Science and Engineering invites May 2015 graduates and their families to a Graduation Luncheon. Graduates will receive a total of three complimentary tickets--this includes the ticket for the graduate's lunch. Additional tickets may be purchased for $10 each.
